snippet.textDisplay:
War horses get spooked the least,

But you can make any horse very brave by holding the control button (wich calms horse)  while on horse back and riding the horse. He or she won't buck you off and it is a bit easier to go past snakes without your horse stopping as much. If its possible, i would play on keyboard so you can put something heavy on that key so your finger doesn't have to hold it down constantly. The control feel smoother and quiker on keyboard and mouse.
